## üîí Compliance & Security

### Real Estate Compliance
- MLS terms of service adherence
- State licensing requirement compliance
- Fair housing law implementation
- RESPA compliance for settlement services

### Mortgage Compliance
- TRID (CFPB) regulation compliance
- NMLS licensing and reporting
- QM (Qualified Mortgage) rule adherence
- HMDA reporting requirements

### Insurance Compliance
- State insurance licensing compliance
- E&O insurance coverage
- Privacy regulation adherence (GLBA)
- Claims handling procedures

### Data Security
- SOC 2 Type II compliance framework
- GDPR and CCPA privacy compliance
- End-to-end encryption for sensitive data
- Regular security audits and penetration testing

## üí∞ Business Model

### Revenue Streams

#### Real Estate Commissions
- Traditional buyer/seller representation (2.5-3% commission)
- Premium blockchain recording service (+0.5% fee)
- International buyer specialized service (premium rates)

#### Mortgage Origination
- Loan origination fees (0.5-1% of loan amount)
- Processing and underwriting fees
- Premium crypto transaction services

#### Insurance Commissions
- Annual policy commissions (10-15% of premium)
- Renewal commissions (2-5% ongoing)
- Bundle optimization consulting fees

#### Technology Services
- White-label platform licensing
- API access for other brokerages
- Blockchain transaction verification services

